title: Mediterranean Sundance - Al Di Meola & Paco De Lucia
description:
Rare Video Excerpt taken from Lorely Festival/Germany :- One Summer Night in 1981
One Year after their Friday Night In San Fransisco at Warfield Theater Performance in 1980.

Two Virtuoso Guitarist 'DiMeola & De Lucia' with their guitar recital "Mediterranean Sundance/Rio Ancho"

Observed & Enjoy their fiery captivating performance.

In my opinion they were without doubt the pioneer in fast guitar neo-classical fusion.

I will be posting soon recital from John McLaughlin & Paco De Lucia also excerpts from the same live concert. 

'So Remember The Name'

Enjoy & Pretty Please With A Sugar On Top!

Keep Seeding So Others Will Get A Chance To View This Clip Too!!
